  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level as a&nbsp;<em>free action</em>, you can cause nanites to flow from your body and coat the striking end of any manufactured melee weapon you wield. When you hit with a melee attack using this weapon, some of the nanites infect the blood of the victim (Poisonâ€”injury;&nbsp;save&nbsp;<em>Fort</em>&nbsp;DC 10 + 1/2 your&nbsp;<em>sorcerer</em>&nbsp;level + your&nbsp;<em>Con</em>&nbsp;modifier;&nbsp;frequency&nbsp;1/round for 6 rounds;&nbsp;effect&nbsp;1&nbsp;<em>Str</em>&nbsp;damage;&nbsp;cure&nbsp;1 save).</p>\n<p>At 5th level, weapons you use with this ability are treated as magical for the purposes of overcoming&nbsp;<em>DR</em>, and the&nbsp;<em>poison</em>&nbsp;also deals 1 point of&nbsp;<em>Constitution damage</em>. At 7th level, the damage increases to 1d2 points of&nbsp;<em>Constitution damage</em>&nbsp;and 1d2 points of&nbsp;<em>Strength damage</em>. At 11th level, the cure becomes two successful saves.</p>\n<p>You can use this ability for a number of rounds per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<em>Charisma</em>&nbsp;modifier; these rounds need not be consecutive.</p>"
